# Ranchero

Initial project skeleton for Ranchero — a 2D farming + roguelite prototype built with Python and pygame-ce.

Run:

1. Create and activate a Python 3.10+ virtualenv
2. pip install -r requirements.txt
3. python -m ranchero.main

This commit provides a working starter: splash screen, cinematic title, main menu (Play / Options / Quit), options to swap Q/E and mouse buttons saved to config, 3 save slots, basic top-down player with camera, hotbar UI, and a day/night timer framework.

